Title: mk_inotify: new plugin to monitor file system operations (linux)
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1465820483
Class: feature

This plugin allows you to check the age of the last file operation
on configurable files and folders. You can check the age of the files or folders
last <tt>create</tt>, <tt>open</tt>, <tt>delete</tt>, <tt>modify</tt> and <tt>access</tt>
operation.

For further information have a look at the agent bakery or the example configuration in
the cfg_examples directory.
